{
  "stem": "9730.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First of all, once Hitler came to power, of course, they-- they fell by the wayside, the non-Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I will tell you something about that in a minute.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we also played some sports, volleyball and-- and things of that nature.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a very easy exchange and banter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I remember those times very fondly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never before, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course, we had seen it coming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I grew up in an era of almost total political strife after World War I.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I saw this monster of the Nazi party grow and grow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And no matter what any of us thought could be done about it, they were not to be stopped, although they had their own setbacks within the progression of that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in-- in the end, we could see that the monster was getting bigger and bigger.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were, of course, many manifestations of anti-Semitism caused by them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For instance, I remember visiting in one town, where they-- surrounded by mountains-- where they had one huge rock, which was the mountain.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one night, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Nazis climbed up that-- that rock.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the morning, there was a huge-- I can't even tell you how large-- swastika.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, of course, everywhere, there were-- there were their Nazi slogans to be found, on-- sometimes on walls of houses, on barns, on wherever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And many of those slogans dealt, you know, with Jews, and-- and what a low form of existence Jews were, I mean, in the-- in the most blatant manner.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we-- we saw what was coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But of course, many Jews deluded themselves, saying, we have lived here all our lives, for generations, in fact.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
